<article id="node-15760">
<h1 >8.1.4.30 Retirement &amp; Widows - Documentation Required</h1>
<h2>Introduction</h2>
<p>The following table lists documentation required with claims for the payments/benefits in the Retirement &amp; Widows grouping. If more detail is required about specific documentation, the third column indicates where you will find this. <a href="../../../acronyms#wp" title="Wife pension">WP</a> and <a href="../../../acronyms#widb" title="Widow B pension">WidB</a> are NOT in the table, as there are no new grants.</p>
<table><thead><tr><th scope="col">Payment Type</th>
<th scope="col">Documentation Required</th>
<th scope="col">More Detail</th>
</tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>
<ul><li>age pension</li>
<li>pension bonus scheme</li>
</ul></td>
<td>
<ul><li>POI</li>
<li>proof of age</li>
<li>details of bank accounts and investments</li>
<li>proof of residence</li>
</ul></td>
<td><a href="../../../2/2/1">2.2.1</a>Verifying Identity<br /><a href="../../../2/2/2">2.2.2</a> Verifying Personal Details<br /><a href="../../../2/2/3">2.2.3</a> Verifying Financial Information<br /><a href="../../../2/2/4">2.2.4</a> Verifying Residence</td>
</tr><tr><td>Pension bonus bereavement payment</td>
<td>
<ul><li>POI (self and deceased)</li>
<li>proof of age (self and deceased)</li>
<li>details of bank accounts and investments (self and deceased)</li>
<li>proof of residence (self and deceased)</li>
<li>proof of death (deceased)</li>
</ul></td>
<td><a href="../../../2/2/1">2.2.1</a> Verifying Identity<br /><a href="../../../2/2/2">2.2.2</a> Verifying Personal Details<br /><a href="../../../2/2/3">2.2.3</a> Verifying Financial Information<br /><a href="../../../2/2/4">2.2.4</a> Verifying Residence<br /><a href="../../../2/2/6">2.2.6</a> Verifying a Death</td>
</tr><tr><td>Widow allowance</td>
<td>
<ul><li>POI</li>
<li>proof of age</li>
<li>details of bank accounts and investments</li>
</ul></td>
<td><a href="../../../2/2/1">2.2.1</a> Verifying Identity<br /><a href="../../../2/2/2">2.2.2</a> Verifying Personal Details<br /><a href="../../../2/2/3">2.2.3</a> Verifying Financial Information</td>
</tr><tr><td>Pension loans scheme</td>
<td>-</td>
<td>-</td>
</tr><tr><td>Special needs pension</td>
<td>
<ul><li>POI</li>
<li>proof of age</li>
<li>Claimants may be requested to provide documentary evidence of income and/or expenses.</li>
</ul><div class="example">
<p><strong>Explanation: </strong>It can be hard to get this information from overseas sources, particularly from non-English speaking countries. While Centrelink aims to be as helpful as possible the onus of proof must be placed on the claimant.</p>
</div>
</td>
<td><a href="../../../2/2/1">2.2.1</a> Verifying Identity<br /><a href="../../../2/2/2">2.2.2</a> Verifying Personal Details<br /><a href="../../../2/2/3">2.2.3</a> Verifying Financial Information</td>
</tr><tr><td>Retirement assistance for farmers scheme</td>
<td>
<ul><li>POI</li>
<li>proof of age</li>
<li>financial statements for the previous 3 years</li>
<li>land transfer documents</li>
<li>the legal title to the farm</li>
</ul></td>
<td><a href="../../../2/2/1">2.2.1</a> Verifying Identity<br /><a href="../../../2/2/2">2.2.2</a> Verifying Personal Details<br /><a href="../../../2/2/3">2.2.3</a> Verifying Financial Information<br /><a href="../../../2/2/9">2.2.9</a> Retirement &amp; Widows Verification (this applies to land transfer &amp; legal title)</td>
</tr><tr><td>Bereavement allowance</td>
<td>proof of death</td>
<td><a href="../../../2/2/6">2.2.6</a> Verifying a Death</td>
</tr></tbody></table><div class="reference">
<p><strong>Act reference:</strong> <a href="https://www.legislation.gov.au/Series/C2004A04121" title="Social Security Act 1991">SSAct</a> section 1185K Does a person satisfy the farmers' income test?, section 17A(7) Retirement assistance for farmers definitions, section 17A(8) To avoid any doubt, section 17A(9) Subject to subsection (11), a qualifying…</p>
<p><strong>Policy reference:</strong> SS Guide <a href="../1">8.1.1</a> Claim Lodgement Provisions</p>
